{"tid":410097,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國外交部：基本法不會在2047年expired，是聯合國登記國際條約","createTime":"2017-09-22T15:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T16:47:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e8dad99ad55befbcacbc43edae06aaffe7146b","tid":410097,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:19:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/HKCPForum/posts/1875429225808569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2FHKCPForum%2Fposts%2F1875429225808569&d=xPvb5zCE1hvAv7d1YEpdmAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=11b8ac19\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/HKCPForum/posts/1875429225808569</a><br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Cultural &amp; Political Forum 文政網新增了 4 張相片。<br />\n<br />\n22小時 &middot; <br />\n<br />\n本會代表及Ben Rogers <span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>與英國外交部代表會面</strong></span>。重點如下：<br />\n<br />\n-<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>外交部表示基本法是沒有限期，不會在2047 expired. The Joint Declaration is an international treaty! 是在聯合國登記。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n-外交部關注抗爭者被判刑超過三個月以上，便失去未來5 年參與選擧權利。<br />\n<br />\n-<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>因抗爭入獄而有criminal record 也可以申請student visa. 上年Home Office 也批student visa 比有criminal record 的 周永康。</strong></span>會就個別情況了解。<br />\n<br />\n-<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>本會一再強調被控告抗爭人士達118 之多。外交部代表有將這段說話紀錄下來。本會將會再寄上118 抗爭者英文名單。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n-meeting 除了大部分時間講DQ6 ，三子入獄及其他在囚抗爭者，<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>也特別提出游梁DQ 後被追人工及被告在立法會內非法集結。佢地聽到被追人工也無言以對。呆呆地。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n-然而外交部仍然相信香港有司法獨立，因為HK Bar Association 係咁講。強調Bar 以前是reputable. 重點是「以前」。<br />\n<br />\n-<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>7 月外交部有派官員出席梁天琦在Henry Jackson Society 及國會的seminars, 收集意見。佢講得出Edward Leung 個名，本會代表有點訝異。但亦代表外交部有誠意收集意見。顯得英文媒體更為重要！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n- 我地有提及BNO. 下回分解。<br />\n<br />\n本會將就 Hong Kong Six Months Report 及更多抗爭者入獄，在十月與外交部再會面。大家有任何意見，請PM 本頁。多謝各位！<br />\n<br />\n圖為外交部照片。每年九月開放日，值得參觀！"},{"pid":"820d290c24444f30abbe8778ee19ecff4ef6fd0e","tid":410097,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12fc68f5472a6fb4e81013499205cd98230b21e","tid":410097,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:25:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">newlife五毛起底</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bzoe9k7q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbzoe9k7q&h=99ae6483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fgzy3w50\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffgzy3w50&h=bf68cf95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53228dd96584e5f5c698c7e723bbec49fea2e66c","tid":410097,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T15:50:57.000Z","msg":"即係點"},{"pid":"0cc4512cd7aa7cf15e54c063476e0a4ce431489f","tid":410097,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:02:17.000Z","msg":"聯合國登記左又有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本呢套憲法，中共有無限既解釋權，佢鍾意點解條法律都得，係框架內根本已經玩晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算聯合國真係捉，咁又點呀，中共係常任理事國，有否決權，根本耐佢唔可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5b02e7d2b5bc8f6a323acff81eb7298768447a","tid":410097,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x